"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe15297111028a253be1893e4bb2312289d4e6d4","tid":1877881,"uid":100986,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"4a77945ac5aca1a3dccf615b8823cd4a942abc21","tid":1877881,"uid":36901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T14:24:06.000Z","msg":"等睇回力鏢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T14:24:54.000Z","msg":"柬埔寨間接幫香港（港共政權想中門大開）<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6aeb810d365c1b73058d4134fa94defb1c2fccc","tid":1877881,"uid":100986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T00:40:36.000Z","msg":"柬埔寨紅森政權：武漢肺炎加油"},{"pid":"7a80dce622179e3e53ce4ade18562709c5f9d88e","tid":1877881,"uid":100986,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T07:20:48.000Z","msg":"威士特丹號郵輪乘客柬埔寨登岸 洪森在場迎接<br />\n2020-02-14 HKT 09:17<br />\n乘客落船後獲洪森（左）迎接及擁抱。（美聯社）<br />\n<br />\n獲准停泊柬埔寨的「威士特丹號」郵輪，數百名乘客今早離開郵輪上岸。首相洪森在場歡迎乘客落船，乘客落船後表現興奮歡呼。<br />\n<br />\n威士特丹號今個月1日由香港出發，原定星期六抵達日本橫濱，但由於憂慮疫情，日本、關島、菲律賓、台灣及泰國都先後拒絕郵輪入境，最終獲柬埔寨當局批准停泊南部西哈努克港。<br />\n<br />\n船上的1455名乘客和大約800名船員，在健康檢查後可以前往首都金邊，然後回家。美國駐柬埔寨使館人員派人協助。郵輪所屬的荷美郵輪公司重申，船上無出現新型肺炎病例。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1508492-20200214.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1508492-20200214.htm&d=2Od897eOL%2Byk6rGVR7zebYR92%2BFrphpe0A3gOlHMrp8%3D&h=e1aa0ad9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1508492-20200214.htm&h=d3853f4f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1508492-20200214.htm</a>"},{"pid":"9472b1a8cb84d17bb4e4d55417eff5f4984ca4b1","tid":1877881,"uid":100986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T08:57:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qpmfjnc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2